# TalkFreeAAC Android Wrapper Plan

This folder prepares the project for Android packaging.

## Recommended path
Use Capacitor after the web app is stable.

## Commands later
```bash
cd web
npm install
npm run build
npm install @capacitor/core @capacitor/cli @capacitor/android
npx cap init TalkFreeAAC com.talkfreeaac.app
npx cap add android
npx cap copy android
npx cap open android
```

## Android package name
Recommended:
`com.talkfreeaac.app`

## App mode
- Local-first
- Offline-capable
- No required account
- No required cloud sync
